---
---

<section
	class="relative h-[704px] overflow-hidden bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,#61CEE2_0%,#98CDCD_36%,#B6C2E3_67%,#AB7BB7_95%)]"
>
	<!-- Pixel grid overlay -->
	<div
		class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(255,255,255,0.14)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(255,255,255,0.14)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:32px_32px]"
		aria-hidden="true"
	>
	</div>

	<!-- Decorative SVGs (white filter against gradient) -->
	<img
		src="/cloud.svg"
		alt=""
		aria-hidden="true"
		class="absolute left-10 top-20 w-32 h-auto brightness-0 invert animate-wiggle"
	/>
	<img
		src="/cloud.svg"
		alt=""
		aria-hidden="true"
		class="absolute right-20 top-28 w-44 h-auto brightness-0 invert animate-wiggle [animation-duration:4s]"
	/>
	<img
		src="/moon.svg"
		alt=""
		aria-hidden="true"
		class="absolute right-16 top-[330px] w-36 h-auto brightness-0 invert animate-wiggle [animation-duration:5s]"
	/>
	<img
		src="/cross.svg"
		alt=""
		aria-hidden="true"
		class="absolute left-[200px] top-16 w-6 h-auto brightness-0 invert animate-wiggle [animation-duration:2s]"
	/>
	<img
		src="/cross.svg"
		alt=""
		aria-hidden="true"
		class="absolute right-[250px] top-[450px] w-5 h-auto brightness-0 invert animate-wiggle [animation-duration:2.5s]"
	/>

	<!-- Content -->
	<div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto pt-28 text-center px-6">
		<h1 class="text-grape-dark font-bold text-7xl leading-none">
			¿Te apasiona la tecnología?
		</h1>
		<p class="text-grape-dark font-bold text-[26px] leading-tight mt-6">
			Amplía tus habilidades técnicas y forma equipo con otras mujeres
		</p>
		<p class="text-ink-2 text-lg leading-snug mt-5 max-w-lg mx-auto">
			Te invitamos a unirte a nuestra comunidad y formar parte de un grupo de
			mujeres que se apoyan y se inspiran mutuamente.
		</p>
		<div class="mt-9">
			<a
				href="#sobre-nosotras"
				class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-snow text-blacky font-bold text-xl border border-blacky rounded-[8px] shadow-[4px_4px_0_0_#1b1b1b] px-5 py-3 hover:-translate-x-px hover:-translate-y-px hover:shadow-[5px_5px_0_0_#1b1b1b] active:translate-x-[3px] active:translate-y-[3px] active:shadow-[1px_1px_0_0_#1b1b1b] transition-[transform,box-shadow] duration-[120ms]"
			>
				Sumate a la comunidad
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
